---
title: Roasted Double Chicken and Goat Cheese with Potato and Greens Salad
description: We've fallen head over heels in love with this quick, colourful and zesty recipe! Lemon adds a citrusy zing to this dish, pairing beautifully with the creaminess of the goat cheese and the crunch of the walnuts!
